{"tid":2137520,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"可能會被玻璃政權禁播的訪問！韓國網上漫畫展的搞手究竟經歷了什麼？","createTime":"2020-08-03T04:02:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-04T11:04:11.000Z","uid":121869,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"11a2ac057cf88776574cae6b330aaa8fb5c0067a","tid":2137520,"uid":121869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T04:02:14.000Z","msg":"幾個月前有班韓國漫畫家搞咗個網上漫畫展嚟撐香港！立場、100毛嗰啲都有報道過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前有班澳洲手足走咗去聯絡韓國搞手，整咗條訪問片，雖然條片柒柒地，不過班手足好有心，想話比一班香港手足知道，全世界都唔會放棄香港，一齊見證着歷史時刻。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊share爆佢，同埋去支持返韓國手足，港韓連線繼續加油。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\">國際線需要你一齊share爆條片</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kw2_-aBusvE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fkw2_-aBusvE&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F6CH8iT5eEApQhURqQe1KTk%3D&h=afdfed32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kw2_-aBusvE</a>"},{"pid":"ca493650953a6df49f10ee20f4ad25a528ff06e9","tid":2137520,"uid":121869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T04:04:10.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e543e6151aaf7dd321ab9c6dad172e5dde31e1","tid":2137520,"uid":121869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T04:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e75c47c04111e7a03e92b7a490e995e63bef7d9","tid":2137520,"uid":121869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T04:04:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif